                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for reducing hydrogen content of molten steel of top-bottom combined blowing converter",
                    "一种降低顶底复吹转炉钢液氢含量的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for reducing the hydrogen content of molten steel of a top-bottom combined blowing converter. The method comprises the following steps: adding molten iron into the converter, and blowing oxygen at the bottom for blowing; when the blowing oxygen amount exceeds 70% of the total blowing oxygen amount, ore is added to adjust the final temperature; when ore does not need to be added for temperature adjustment after TSC, bottom blowing of oxygen is stopped after the top lance stops blowing at the end point, bottom blowing of argon is stopped, stirring is conducted for 0.2-0.8 min, and then tapping is conducted; when ore needs to be added for temperature adjustment after TSC, ore is added again for cooling, the oxygen blowing amount of T * (90-110) m < 3 > is reduced, blowing of a top lance and a bottom lance is stopped at the same time, and tapping is conducted after bottom blowing argon stirring is conducted for T * (0.8-1.2) min; and T is the tonnage of the re-added ore. The method is high in dehydrogenation rate and simple and convenient to operate through strong stirring by blowing argon from the bottom; bottom blowing argon replaces bottom oxygen, so that natural gas entering molten steel for cracking and hydrogen increasing when end point carbon is low is reduced; and blowing is stopped in advance, the end point carbon content is slightly increased, hydrogen increase in the last stage of blowing is reduced, and moist moisture in the cold charge is counteracted."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种降低顶底复吹转炉钢液氢含量的方法，其方法工艺为：转炉加入铁水后底吹氧气进行吹炼；当吹炼氧量超过吹炼总氧量的70%，加入矿石调节终点温度；当TSC后不需要加入矿石调温时，终点顶枪停吹后停止底吹氧气，底吹氩气搅拌0.2～0.8min后出钢；当TSC后需要加入矿石调温时，再次添加矿石进行降温，减少T×(90～110)m3吹氧量，顶枪、底枪同时停吹，底吹氩气搅拌T×(0.8～1.2)min后出钢；所述T为再次添加矿石吨数。本方法通过底部吹氩强烈搅拌，脱氢速率快，操作简便；底吹氩替代底氧，减少终点碳低时天然气进入钢水裂解增氢；点吹加冷料的炉次，提前停吹，少量提高终点碳含量，减少吹炼末期增氢，抵消冷料中潮湿水分。"
                }
